high_descs: Turn to your left facing the cabinet beside the stove
Open the cabinet and pick up the sponge then close the cabinet
Turn right then face the stove on your left
Put the sponge in the pan
Pick up the pan with sponge at the stove
Turn right then stand on the counter beside the sink
Put the pan with sponge on the counter beside the tomato
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with sponge on the counter

high_descs: Turn left and face the counter with the knife in front of you.
Open the cabinet under the knife in front of you, take out the green sponge and close the cabinet.
Turn right then face the stove on your left.
Place the sponge inside the pot on the stove in front of you.
Take the pot from the stove in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink in front of you.
Place the pot on the counter by the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place the pot with a sponge near the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the counter to the left of the stove
Open the cabinet that is to the left of the stove and pick up the sponge inside then close the door
Turn right and walk to the stove, then turn left and face the stove
Place the sponge inside the pan on the front right burner
Pick up the pan that contains the sponge
Turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the sink then turn right so you are facing the counter on the other side of the sink
Place the pan containing the sponge on the other side of the sink, in front of the tomato
anns.task_desc: Place a pan containing a sponge on a counter
